            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[拳头]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_quantou-81f684d5ed.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>很抱歉，你的卫要耽误30秒，今天，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%82%BE%E8%84%8F%E6%97%A5%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#世界肾脏日#</span></a> ，给大家总结了最作死的7个伤肾行为：<br>1⃣️憋尿<br>2⃣️不爱喝水<br>3⃣️喝太多含糖饮料<br>4⃣️饮食太咸+大鱼大肉<br>5⃣️睡眠不足，过于劳累<br>6⃣️吸烟<br>7⃣️乱吃药<br><br>日常一定要多喝水，每人每日应饮水1500-1800毫升！肾脏损伤不可逆，保护“腰子”，从现在做起<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbtn44cuqcj20at0cu75p.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
